### ğŸ“¦ Sample Request Body for Register/Login:

**Register:**

```
POST /api/auth/register
{
  "name": "Thiyo",
  "email": "thiyo@example.com",
  "password": "yourpassword"
}
```

**Login:**

```
POST /api/auth/login
{
  "email": "thiyo@example.com",
  "password": "yourpassword"
}
```

